{"id":845041475,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"5 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1668667961,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"2 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/845041475/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Rectangle Area","memory":"41.9 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int computeArea(int ax1, int ay1, int ax2, int ay2, int bx1, int by1, int bx2, int by2) {\n        int a1=(ax2-ax1)*(ay2-ay1);//area of rectangle 1\n        int a2=(bx2-bx1)*(by2-by1);//area of rectangle 2\n\n        //co-ordinates of intersecting rectangle\n        int x5 = Math.max(ax1, bx1);\n        int y5 = Math.max(ay1, by1);\n        int x6 = Math.min(ax2, bx2);\n        int y6 = Math.min(ay2, by2);\n\n        int x=x6-x5;\n        int y=y6-y5;\n        int a3=x*y;//area of intersecting rectangle\n        if(x<0 || y<0){//means both rectangle don't intersects\n            a3=0;\n        }\n        \n        return a1+a2-a3;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"rectangle-area","has_notes":false}
